title: Venetica NTSC/U Xbox 360
description:
Venetica:

Region      : NTSC/U                Languages: English        
Size        : 1 DVD                 Genre    : RPG         
Platform    : XBOX 360              Date     : 01/2011

About:

A woman with the powers of death may be the only one who can preserve life in this haunting action-RPG adventure. In Renaissance-era Venice the job of death - and the powers that come with it - are given to a human being chosen by a secret council. But the council's latest choice, Victor, grows power hungry and begins to unleash horrifying creatures on the helpless city. The council turns to Scarlett, a descendant of Death itself and the one person who may possess the power to stop Victor. Walk between the worlds of the living and the dead as you harness Twilight Powers to restore balance to the world.
